headline: Mama's Creations, Inc. (MAMA) Tops Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Mama's Creations, Inc. (MAMA) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +400.00% and +8.66%, respectively, for the quarter ended October 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
